{"tid":964810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"約三十名不同派系港獨派參與民陣遊行  港獨派：兩者唔同，同民陣遊行有分別","createTime":"2019-01-01T14:58:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T09:14:23.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"035ceac65ccbdc9b9794015dc14f6e21beb36d59","tid":964810,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435956-20190101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435956-20190101.htm&d=97esOlL2cJgV1GPY69%2F%2F4xv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=ad8bc9a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1435956-20190101.htm&h=3a4af5fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1435956-20190101.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n約30名支持港獨人士參與民陣元旦遊行，他們未有跟從民陣路線進入政府總部東翼前地，改為於金鐘統一中心附近解散。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣線召集人梁頌恆表示，改變遊行終點，目的在於顯示與民陣的分別。他說組織支持香港獨立，而非無了期要求「我要真普選」，認為爭取香港獨立更為現實，亦不打算與保安員或警員有衝突。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆又表示，只要仍有自由，都會爭取香港獨立。他提到組織的倉庫日前被人爆竊，失去部分旗幟。"},{"pid":"b484fa7b7c541f13f2154f983e6560333e6618fc","tid":964810,"uid":25641,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T15:00:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8c901498f6bf3eef2224d6884e6de74937aa4ef","tid":964810,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b3978a8124d2576baa81552ea2d86eb04e1e5b","tid":964810,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-01T15:31:04.000Z","msg":"30名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 共諜冇曬經費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 